# exponent

- _exponent(p)_

Answer the largest exponent of the polynomial _p_,
also called the `degree` of the polynomial.

```
>>> let p = UnivariatePolynomial([1 2 3]);
>>> (p.exponent, p.degree)
(2, 2)
```

